attributes.tentangSaya:
I'm a Software Engineer, I help people build the software they need. And I also really like learning new things like learning the latest technology.

And currently Javascript and Typescript are the programming languages that I often use, and I often use frontend frameworks like React and Vue Js in developing Web Applications. To build a mobile app I use Ionic & React Native as a framework
attributes.kontak: Connect with me through my social media accounts
attributes.projek: The following are web application projects and mobile application projects that I have worked on, both individual projects and my work projects. These are the projects I have worked on
attributes.riwayatProjek: Projects That Have Been Worked On

attributes.deskripsi: Build Web App with react, next js, chakra ui and tailwind css and Ionic

Create a website application using the react js and vue js frameworks, create an android application with react native & ionic, set up a web server with nginx, set up a postgresql database version 12 and initialize the configuration on the production server
Work as a freelance part time to make Website App and Mobile App using Javascript Env
